            <div type="transcript" id="F909A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Because the Bee may<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 blameless hum</l>
                    <l>For Thee a Bee do<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 I become </l>
                    <l>List even unto Me - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Because the Flowers<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 unafraid </l>
                    <l>May lift a look on<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 thine, a Maid</l>
                    <l>Alway a Flower would be - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Nor Robins, Robins need<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 not hide </l>
                    <l>When Thou opon their<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Crypts intrude </l>
                    <l>So Wings bestow on Me </l>
                    <l>Or Petals, or a Dower<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 of Buzz</l>
                    <l>That Bee to ride - or<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Flower of Furze<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>I that way worship Thee - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
